<h2>Experience and Advancement. </h2>
<h3>Gaining Experience</h3>
A Warrior can gain experience in a number of different ways, <br>
The most common is +1 Exp for surviving a match, that both Henchmen and Heroes get if they managed to not be die during a game, this even counts if they were knocked Out of Action.
<br>Heroes gain +1 Exp for every enemy they take Out of Action during a match
<br>Leaders gain +1 Exp for winning a match.
<br>Other ways of detailing gaining exp are also listed in any scenario played and there are some ways that will pop up in special circumstances such as a 66 on the Injury Chart.
<h3>Underdog Bonus</h3>
