<h3> Experience Milestones </h3>
<h4>Heroes:</h4>
<p>Some Heroes start at a set level of experience, this is taken into accounts with their characteristics / skills so you should not roll of advancement of the warrior for this experience. <br>
Heroes gain an Advancement at the experience milestones of. <br>
Exp: <em>2,4,6,8,11,13,17,20,24,28,32,36</em> and then every consecutive <em>5</em> experience after that. </p>
<h4>Henchmen </h4>
<p>Henchmen start with no experience.
Henchmen gain an Advancement at the experience milestones of.<br>
Exp: <em>2, 5, 9, 14</em> and then every consecutive <em>5</em> experience after that </p>
<h3>Advancement</h3>
<p>When a Warrior reaches an Experience Milestone they make a roll on the applicable Advancement chart.</p>

